Text: FW FW NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORPPlease see the attached correspondence between Stephanie Panus of Enron and myself I only received the required original Notary Certificate from Stephanie this past Friday although it was first requested back in December Now that I have it I am expediting the process of obtaining the Apostille and sending the Agreement off to our Zurich office for signature We should have your originals to you by next week sometime Please do not hesitate to call me if you have questions about any of this My number is Thank you Kimberly Dautenhahn Original Message From Dautenhahn Kimberly Sent Thursday March PM To Subject RE FW NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP Stephanie I received your voicemail of earlier this week I did not receive the package containing the notary certificate only the fax In addition the certificate which you sent to me is not in the form which we requested It may be sufficient I will have to check with our service company However I will at least need an original copy of the certificate which you faxed to me Please make sure it is sent to my attention at our new address Lehman Brothers One World Financial Center th Floor New York NY Thank you Kimberly Original Message From SMTP Sent Wednesday March PM To Dautenhahn Kimberly Subject Re FW NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP Kimberly I have tracked down the notarized certificate from our corporate office and am faxing a copy to you I will also forward the original in overnight delivery Sorry again for the delay on our end Dautenhahn Kimberly on PM To cc Subject FW NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP Stephanie Richard Weiss forwarded to me your email from today The reason we have not sent you the executed Master Agreement is because it has not been executed Switzerland will not execute the document without an Apostille and we cannot obtain an Apostille until you send us the Notarial Certificate as per the attached messages Please advise as to the status of this at your earliest convenience Thanks Kimberly Original Message From SMTP Sent Wednesday January PM To Dautenhahn Kimberly Subject Re NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP Kimberly Sorry for the delay I did receive the package and sent the certificate to our corporate department for execution since it is for Enron Corp I am checking with them and will let you know the status Stephanie Panus Sr Legal Specialist Enron North America Corp Smith Street Suite Houston Texas ph fax Dautenhahn Kimberly ehmanCOM on PM To STEPHANIE NRONCOM STEPHANIE NRONCOM cc Subject NOTARIAL CERTIFICATE FOR ENRON CORP Stephanie On December I sent you a package containing a Notarial Certificate which needs to be completed and returned to us I have yet to receive anything or to get any response from you Please advise if you received this package and when I should be expecting the completed certificate Until we have it we cannot obtain the Apostille which is required in order for any of your documents to be used in Switzerland If you have any questions regarding this please contact me at your earliest convenience Thank you Kimberly Kimberly A Dautenhahn Transaction Management
